Class Imaging

java.lang.Object
model.Appointment
model.Imaging
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
public class Imaging extends Appointment
Represents an imaging appointment, extending the Appointment class. This class is used for scheduling imaging procedures such as X-rays, ultrasounds, or CAT scans. It includes details about the appointment date, timeslot, patient, provider, and the specific imaging room.
Author:
Gursimar Singh
